                       <div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data">

                        <span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text">

                         <div data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height: none; height: 300px;">

                          <div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content" style="padding-bottom: 20px;"> <span>As I read in reviews the picture quality is just so, so. Only a few manufacturers make 43? models and you have to take what you can get. The screen has too much glare. I found it virtually impossible to watch the picture on a sunny day without closing the drapes. It is no pleasure at night with room lights on. My old TV had NO concerns. The model is plagued with software problems. Upon arrival, it was already out of date. Virtually no apps are preloaded. It took me 5 hours just to download the 15 apps I do use. Voice command was of little help in finding them. Until you have Tubi setup it doesnt know the difference between that and To be? which gets you nowhere. I love remotes where the buttons are placed so perfectly you dont need to look at them and arrive at the right place. This is not one of them. If you get lazy and dont look, expect to lose your show. The home button takes you to home sometimes. And often times it never will. The same is true with other buttons. You will have to find your workarounds when they dont. The Software is very unstable. If you click on your streaming menu live? TV it takes you automatically to the Pluto app, even if you never had that in mind. And good luck trying to get to where you do have in mind. On Pluto, the program disappears every 10 minutes or so and up pops a screen saver causing you to lose your show. Waiting wont take you back, you have to find your own way back. And expect to be annoyed as you miss a lot of your show. Let me assure you this is not Plutos problem. Ive watched it for years. TCL Support is of no help. Their registration page requires the model no, serial no, date of purchase, date of delivery, and purchase price. After entering all the info up popped REJECTED? which accuses me of Maybe you tried to change something you didn't have access to.? I spent so many hours in frustration I eventually emailed TCL support and asked them to register the TV for me. Would you believe their answer is Rest assured, we are here to help. However, as much as we wanted to register the TV on your behalf, we do not have that option.? I wrote and asked for a US mail address to register it and did not get a reply. If they cant handle that what can they do??</span> 

                          </div>

    if (isIE) {

      for (var i=0; i<jsCssAssets.length; i++) {

        new Image().src = jsCssAssets[i];

      }

    }

    else if (isFireFox) {

      for (var i=0; i<jsCssAssets.length; i++) {

        var o =  document.createElement("object");

        o.data = jsCssAssets[i];

        o.width = o.height = 0;

        document.body.appendChild(o);

      }

    }

}



    var onload = function () {

        setTimeout(prefetchTYPAssets, 2000);

    };

    if (window.addEventListener) {

        window.addEventListener("load", onload);

    } else if (window.attachEvent) { /* for <= IE 8 */

        window.attachEvent("onload", onload);

    }

     <script type="text/javascript">(function ($Nav) {

"use strict";



if (typeof $Nav === 'undefined' || $Nav === null || typeof $Nav.when !== 'function') {

    return;

}



$Nav.when('$', 'data', 'flyout.yourAccount', 'sidepanel.csYourAccount',

          'config')

    .run("BuyitAgain-YourAccount-SidePanel",

    function ($, data, yaFlyout, csYourAccount, config) {

        if (config.disableBuyItAgain) {

            return;

        }

        var render = function (data) {

            if (data.dramResult) {

                var widgetHtml = data.dramResult;

                navbar.sidePanel({

                    flyoutName: 'yourAccount',

                    data: {html: widgetHtml}

                });

            }

        };



        var renderBuyItAgain = function (biaData) {

            if (csYourAccount) {

                csYourAccount.register(render, biaData);

            } else {

                render(biaData);

            }

        };



        var truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout = function() {

            if (window.P) {

                P.when('A', 'a-truncate').execute(function(A, truncate) {

                    var truncateElements = A.$('.a-truncate');

                    A.each(truncateElements, function(element) {

                        truncate.get(element).update();

                    });

                    var recommendationsWidget = document.getElementById('bia-hcb-widget');

                    if (recommendationsWidget) { 

                        var navFlyout = recommendationsWidget.parentElement;

                        var navFlyoutPaddingBottom = parseInt(window.getComputedStyle(navFlyout).getPropertyValue('padding-bottom'));

                        var navFlyoutContentHeight = navFlyout.clientHeight - navFlyoutPaddingBottom;

                        while (recommendationsWidget.offsetHeight > navFlyoutContentHeight && recommendationsWidget.offsetHeight > 0){

                            var recommendations = recommendationsWidget.querySelectorAll('.biaNavFlyoutFaceout');

                            if (recommendations.length <= 1) {

                                break;

                            }

                            var lastRecommendation = recommendations[recommendations.length - 1];

                            lastRecommendation.parentElement.removeChild(lastRecommendation);

                        }

                    }

               });

            }

        };



        yaFlyout.sidePanel.onData(truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout);

        yaFlyout.onShow(truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout);



    yaFlyout.onRender(function() {

            $.ajax({

                url: '/gp/bia/external/bia-hcb-ajax-handler.html',

                data: {"biaHcbRid":"TX6RQW263B6VYJ8P8T67"},

                dataType: 'json',

                timeout: 4*1000,

                success: renderBuyItAgain,

                error: function (jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown) {

                }

            });

        });

    });

})(window.$Nav);</script>
